summary: Nude skin for Khajiit females that change the front of the character. Less fur to cover stuff.
descriptionHtml:
This mod makes the Khajiit females show some frontal nudity unobscured by fur. I used a part of the human nude skin made by Thepal (mainly the breast part of it), the rest is vanilla or made by me.

This mod is just a skin, to show it correctly you might need a nude mod such as the one made by Thepal (link below). Just make sure to apply my Khajiit mod last.

http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=70
author: Nalim666
